    • Class Test.TestCase5 extends javax.swing.JFrame implements Serializable

      • Serialized Fields

        • ef

          ElectricFence ef
          Creates new form TestCase5 Draws both drone and electric fence on canvas. Once the add ball button is click it will draw a ball on the canvas. Shows how they interact with each other. If the fence is off the drone will move away from fence when hit. If the fence is on the drone will be destroyed when hit. If the fence is off the ball will bounce off the fence. If the fence is on the ball will be destroyed.
